21:03.162 --> 21:04.897 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Hari Sreenivasan has that.

21:04.930 --> 21:08.033 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Despite all
the warnings
over the years, you may be
surprised that,

21:08.067 --> 21:12.471 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
for the first time, the
